Solved by add the function ParametersNameList() in my script:
```
def parametersNamesList(tpl):
	pnamelist = []
	for p in tpl.params:
		pnamelist.append(p.name.strip())
	return pnamelist
		
def removeTplParametersExceptThis(tpl, keys):
	pnamelist = parametersNamesList(tpl)		
	for p in pnamelist:
		if p not in keys:
			tpl.remove(p)

removeTplParametersExceptThis(newtemplate, ('автор', 'заглавие', 'статья', 'том', 'страницы', 'ref'))
```
looks like it works

